chord.project.analyses.rhs
Class RHSAnalysis<PE extends IEdge,SE extends IEdge>

Direct Known Subclasses:
ThreadEscapeFullAnalysis, TypeStateAnalysis
public abstract class RHSAnalysis<PE extends IEdge,SE extends IEdge>
extends JavaAnalysis

Implementation of the Reps-Horwitz-Sagiv algorithm for context-sensitive dataflow analysis. Relevant system properties: - chord.rhs.merge = [lossy|pjoin|naive] (default = lossy) - chord.rhs.order = [bfs|dfs] (default = bfs) - chord.rhs.trace = [none|any|shortest] (default = none) - chord.rhs.timeout = N milliseconds (default N = 0, no timeouts)

Author:
Mayur Naik (mhn@cs.stanford.edu)
